{"tid":1845053,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【B-I-O-H-A-Z-A-R-D】 北京醫生只係開會就全部感染曬","createTime":"2020-01-27T02:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:05:04.000Z","uid":242537,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eef6c44f05f31b8fcfaac4dd6338508ad5ec34f3","tid":1845053,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:45:07.000Z","msg":"立場報道2020/1/26 &mdash; 8:43<br />\n<br />\n北京市衛健委確認，三名醫生確診患新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎。當中兩人曾赴武漢出差，一人曾於開會時，坐在已感染醫生隔鄰。<br />\n<br />\n醫生王某某，男，1月8日赴武漢工幹，16日返京，當日就有發熱和呼吸道症狀，20日就診，21日確診；<br />\n<br />\n醫生魯某某，男，1月10日赴武漢工幹，11日返京，14日有發熱症狀，20日就診，21日確診；<br />\n<br />\n醫生閻某，男，1月3日至10日曾到大連、吉林白山、長春等地旅行，14日參加會議時與上述病例魯某某座位相鄰，18日有發熱症狀，20日就診，25日確診。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/25/c6/7c/25c67c9f0c3bf4b171aa6b418b8bcd62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F25%2Fc6%2F7c%2F25c67c9f0c3bf4b171aa6b418b8bcd62.png&h=be440fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTEQIQhw9a9En5wh9HD5-648-0vhx-XAX2kAPKEwekXBNMe1LzA&amp;s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTEQIQhw9a9En5wh9HD5-648-0vhx-XAX2kAPKEwekXBNMe1LzA%26s&h=a695bbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qj7cCxGusYM/XJYCt9rTCII/AAAAAAAA4vY/wwXCC1QK74EAStqo2fOQy5Qpv81qfHk2ACKgBGAs/w700/1553334844_509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-qj7cCxGusYM%2FXJYCt9rTCII%2FAAAAAAAA4vY%2FwwXCC1QK74EAStqo2fOQy5Qpv81qfHk2ACKgBGAs%2Fw700%2F1553334844_509.jpg&h=085b2186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71fb727a458bd9fe0ea4d9a5980f8de68507c91d","tid":1845053,"uid":126621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"絕症+傳染性高<br />\n你放大陸人落黎醫做乜鳩<br />\n完全無醫嘅價值<br />\n八宗你隔離左唔醫就死八個<br />\n醫嘅話點只死八個呀dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫症爆發一定係隔離佢地再燒死佢地<br />\n由古到今都係燒村控制疫情架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396919a1c75cb9131089d4a8e4df12ba74c2f0ff","tid":1845053,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"第二個醫生只係留左係武漢一晚<br />\n<br />\n返到北京就傳染俾第三個醫生"},{"pid":"44f9425a83e779e02d151081bc54bc0fbb68a696","tid":1845053,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mR9JZ4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmR9JZ4Z.jpg&h=a325ec3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFsznik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFsznik.jpg&h=8ec7e37e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3XrXRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3XrXRF.jpg&h=9f9d87d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad452e7cefe8314bbc40034cdb833fcdeb92cb28","tid":1845053,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcfcf29fee6e4e627d026893ebc3fb451cedd0d","tid":1845053,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /